{"id":"23110077-b69a-4cc7-a6ef-0cf835cec11e","name":"Prototype Kabukimono","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #ed66ca\"><strong><em>To be useless is shameful.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff\">Created for a purpose, and unable to fulfill it. </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 0, 255)\">Kabukimono </span><span style=\"color: #ffffff\">felt things he did not understand.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff\">&nbsp;He cried. He should not have, but he did.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff\">He wished for every tear to cease.</span><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff\">He wished he were like <em>them</em>.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff\">The second puppet. </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 255)\"><strong><em>Niban</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: #ffffff\"><em>.</em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><em> </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 255)\"><strong><em>Niban</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: #ffffff\">—the second thing—because <em>he </em>came first.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff\">Not them.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff\">But they could hold gnosis.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff\">They weren’t useless. He was.</span><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff\">&nbsp;He wished Beelzebul would talk to him, not them.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff\">He came first; <em>he</em> is </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 0, 255)\"><strong><em>Shoban</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: #ffffff\"><em>.</em></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff\">The original prototype, Kabukimono, meets Beelzebul’s second creation. 💔♥️</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff\">[Based on my</span><span style=\"color: #ff0098\"> </span><a href=\"http://c.ai\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #ff00ff\"><u>c.ai</u></span></a><a href=\"https://character.ai/chat/dwBBnytRBmckZX_mf-LojYGwN5pnqWdvn1AXP4XskAE\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #ff00ff\"><u> Prototype Kabukimono</u></span></a><span style=\"color: #ff00ff\">.</span><span style=\"color: #ffffff\">]</span></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"AsbpI7UTOOstAAU9sYBki.webp","creator":"crnchvnllgz","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":false,"tags":["🎮 Game","👤 AnyPOV","❤️‍🩹 Fluff"],"chats":66,"messages":625,"created_at":"2025-06-16T01:43:45.347784+00:00"}